    "It is crucial to comprehend various CNN components and their respective applications in order to learn about the developments in CNN architecture in computer vision (Bhatt et al. 2021).",
    "The role of these components in a CNN architecture is covered in brief in this section.",
    "Before being input to CNN, the raw data needs to be preprocessed.",
